{"tid":1050372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理工集會 今晚七時至八時三十分   審訊制度不公 要求撤回處分","createTime":"2019-03-07T00:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T13:10:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":61,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"534fbdd5889ff7784e96744ae09bdc262b7abf73","tid":1050372,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"理工集會 今晚七時至八時三十分 <br />\n<br />\n審訊制度不公 要求撤回處分 <br />\n<br />\n日期：三月七日 （星期四）<br />\n時間：晚上七時至八時三十分 <br />\n地點：香港理工大學孫志新紀念廣場 （M Core對開）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkpusu/photos/a.441112069305462/2106696549413664/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=EH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkpusu%2Fphotos%2Fa.441112069305462%2F2106696549413664%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D57%26refid%3D52%26ref%3Dpage_internal%26__tn__%3DEH-R&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=839eb0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkpusu/photos/a.441112069305462/2106696549413664/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=EH-R</a>"},{"pid":"0132bd5b92bbc44f79ebd4c8eb34705d5b11617a","tid":1050372,"uid":202139,"like":8,"dislike":42,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:54:09.000Z","msg":"要上堂，不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9848c199c8d10cdaa6bf7c132de21d373094a3dc","tid":1050372,"uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:10:39.000Z","msg":"[突發]理大教授插水屈學生片段曝光<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1047418\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1047418</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2175527479425721&amp;id=507540123055378&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2175527479425721%26id%3D507540123055378%26_rdr&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=59b49db5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2175527479425721&amp;id=507540123055378&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"89de1c00f029a7225505465a43a52e9c4e0ae6c9","tid":1050372,"uid":35014,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeec47d3b026ddd3947e3ff9701f6d9ebabca747","tid":1050372,"uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"香港理大學生會 HKPUSU<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【審訊制度不公 要求撤回處分】<br />\n<br />\n學生紀律委員會在聆訊期間，在缺乏法理基礎下，僭以法律之名胡作非為。學生紀律聆訊制度一塌糊塗，毫不尊重學生之餘，亦反映出理工大學制度流弊叢生。<br />\n<br />\n根據是次聆訊結果，鄭悅婷及李傲然被判社會服務令。去屆理大學生會會長林穎恒被罰即時停學一年，而碩士生何俊謙更被勒令退學，終生不再獲理大錄取，懲罰與行為輕重完全不合乎比例原則。是次判決不僅剝奪了涉事理大同學之權利，更嚴重打壓學生言論及表達自由。因此，我等要求理大重新檢視判決理據及學生紀律聆訊制度，並撤回對同學的無理處分。為此，我等將於星期四晚上舉辦集會，集會詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：三月七日 （星期四）<br />\n時間：晚上七時至八時三十分<br />\n地點：香港理工大學孫志新紀念廣場 （M Core對開）<br />\n發言單位：待定<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位：<br />\n香港理工大學學生會<br />\n<br />\n集會聯絡人：<br />\n理大學生會幹事會<br />\n內務副會長 胡國泓 6488 2739<br />\n外務副會長 李晃榮 9435 0545<br />\n外務秘書 周美芝 9328 6315<br />\n<br />\n謹此呼籲各位出席集會，支援理大同學之抗爭行動，共同捍衛岌岌可危的學生自治權利，並還涉事同學一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpusu/photos/a.441112069305462/2106696549413664/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=EH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpusu%2Fphotos%2Fa.441112069305462%2F2106696549413664%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D57%26refid%3D52%26ref%3Dpage_internal%26__tn__%3DEH-R&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=632e38dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpusu/photos/a.441112069305462/2106696549413664/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=EH-R</a>"},{"pid":"a536134040c9a7dfa26229aa1beb120c09716891","tid":1050372,"uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"到咗理工大學， 見到搭緊台。"},{"pid":"06f2f8bcd21054dbea264e24039a5b69dd699016","tid":1050372,"uid":62809,"like":2,"dislike":6,